                <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/655">Centurion (2010)</a></h1>

                <h2>24 Oct 2010, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                <p>Hadrian’s Wall, the ninth legion are ordered north in a final attempt to conquer Caledonia. In the ensuing battle only 7 legionnaires survive&hellip;
They most now fight their way south to the safety of the other legions, whilst pursued by vengeance filled Scottish warriors.
A rough, tough, gory, swords and sandals action adventure.
</p>

